snippet.title: DARK and DEEP Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow my solo dev journey here: https://linktr.ee/walterwoodsdev
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2493360/Dark_and_Deep/
 
A conspiracy podcast drags you into a hauntingly illustrated world of mystery and terror. Reveal secrets and horrors with mystical frames given to you by a strange observer. Dark and Deep is a first person cosmic horror game with a focus on puzzles and exploration.

Coming to Steam August 2024!
